@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.71 / wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.61)))
    v2 = (v2 * (wp.exp(v0 + 0.06) - wp.sin(v1 + 0.07)))
    v0 = (v1 - (0.65 / (v1 + 0.95 + tmp + 0.50)))
    v0 = v0
    v1 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.27) * (tmp + 0.18 / v2 + 0.21)) - wp.cos((v2 + 0.61 * v1 + 0.14)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(v2) / (v2 / (tmp + 0.67 + tmp + 0.04)))
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
